  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "1. SETUP: Install fonts and override CSS variables in index.css immediately to establish the dark theme.",
    "2. GLASSMORPHISM: Do not use default opaque cards. Create a reusable 'GlassCard' component that applies the backdrop-blur and border styles defined in visual_enhancers.",
    "3. CHARTS: Use Recharts. Customise the 'Tooltip' to be a glass card. Use the 'brand' colors for lines/bars. Hide cartesian grids or make them 5% opacity.",
    "4. LAYOUT: Use the Bento Grid for the Overview dashboard. It must look designed, not just a list of boxes.",
    "5. SHAP VALUES: When displaying SHAP explanations, use horizontal bar charts. Red bars = Risk increase, Green bars = Success increase.",
    "6. TABLES: For the Student Explorer, use Shadcn Table but style the header with a transparent background and sticky positioning.",
    "7. ANIMATIONS: Add 'framer-motion' layout animations. Entering a page should stagger the appearance of cards."
  ],
  "universal_guidelines": [
    "You tend to converge toward generic, 'on distribution' outputs. Avoid this.",
    "Dark colors look good when used independently without gradients. DO NOT use dark colors as gradients.",
    "Don't make generic centered layouts. Use grids.",
    "Create depth through layered design elements with z-index hierarchy.",
    "Use glass-morphism effects with backdrop filters (12-24px blur).",
    "You MUST NOT apply universal transition (transition: all).",
    "You MUST NOT center align the app container.",
    "Always use modern button styles (pill-shaped or sharp).",
    "NEVER use AI assistant Emoji characters.",
    "Every interaction needs micro-animations.",
    "Use 2-3x more spacing than feels comfortable.",
    "All interactive elements MUST include data-testid."
  ]
}